{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be cozy and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Forge Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4e8e5; /* A soft, warm off-white */\n            color: #333;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a64d4d 0%, #6b2e2e 100%); /* Deep red gradient */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        main {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            border-left: 5px solid #a64d4d; /* Red accent */\n            background-color: #fffaf9; /* Very light red-tinted background */\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        section:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #6b2e2e; /* Darker red */\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        p {\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .game-list {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\n        }\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border: 1px solid #e0c8c8; /* Light red border */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            width: 250px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);\n        }\n        .game-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 150px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\n            border: 2px solid #a64d4d; /* Red border for images */\n        }\n        .game-card h3 {\n            margin: 0.5rem 0;\n            color: #a64d4d;\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n        }\n        .game-card p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #6b2e2e; /* Dark red */\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 1rem;\n            margin-top: auto;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            box-shadow: 0 -2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        a {\n            color: #a64d4d; /* Red links */\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        a:hover {\n            color: #330f0f; /* Darker red on hover */\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .social-links a {\n            margin: 0 0.5rem;\n            color: #fff;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n        .social-links a:hover {\n            color: #e0c8c8;\n        }\n        #contact-form {\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        #contact-form input,\n        #contact-form textarea {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 400px;\n            padding: 0.8rem;\n            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\n            border: 1px solid #e0c8c8;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        #contact-form button {\n            background-color: #a64d4d;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #6b2e2e;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Crimson Forge Studios</h1>\n        <p>Crafting Worlds, One Pixel at a Time</p>\n    </header>\n    <main>\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Welcome to Crimson Forge Studios, where passion meets pixel! We are a small, dedicated team of game developers who believe in creating immersive and memorable gaming experiences. Our cozy atmosphere fuels our creativity, allowing us to pour our hearts into every project.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"games\">\n            <h2>Our Games</h2>\n            <div class=\"game-list\">\n                <div class=\"game-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/a64d4d/ffffff?text=Game+1\" alt=\"Game Title 1\">\n                    <h3>Echoes of the Hearth</h3>\n                    <p>A cozy life-sim with crafting and exploration.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/a64d4d/ffffff?text=Game+2\" alt=\"Game Title 2\">\n                    <h3>Crimson Keep</h3>\n                    <p>A charming roguelike with deep narrative elements.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x150/a64d4d/ffffff?text=Game+3\" alt=\"Game Title 3\">\n                    <h3>Starlight Bistro</h3>\n                    <p>A whimsical restaurant management game.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have questions, feedback, or just want to say hello? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Forge Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <div class=\"social-links\">\n            <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Twitter\"><i class=\"fab fa-twitter\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Facebook\"><i class=\"fab fa-facebook-f\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Instagram\"><i class=\"fab fa-instagram\"></i></a>\n        </div>\n        <p>Designed with <span style=\"color: #a64d4d;\">&hearts;</span></p>\n    </footer>\n    <script src=\"https://kit.fontawesome.com/your-fontawesome-kit.js\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Message sent! Thanks for reaching out.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}